description: This file is the entry point for a React application. It imports React, ReactDOM, a CSS stylesheet, and the main App component. It creates a React root and renders the App component wrapped in StrictMode into a DOM element with the ID 'root'.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering React elements into a DOM node.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React elements into the container associated with the root.
